{"tid":737783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國商務部：關稅新清單完全不可接受","createTime":"2018-07-11T05:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T05:32:49.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8506ea2c859dc57d3954b600d390019d579673f8","tid":737783,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰火升溫，美國政府周二（10日）列出新清單，擬對華總值2000億美元（約1.56萬億港元）、逾6031種商品加徵10%關稅，當中包括「中國製造2025」商品，最快9月生效。美國國內的零售業協會批評，總統特朗普新一波舉動，最終只會「懲罰」美國的家庭。中國商務部新聞發言人周三（11日）回應稱，美方以加速升級的方式公布徵稅清單，是完全不可接受的，中方對此表示嚴正抗議。<br />\n<br />\n貿易代表萊蒂澤表示：「在逾一年的時間內，政府一直耐心地呼籲中國停止不公平的政策，開發市場及參與真正的市場競爭。但中國未有理會我們，反而開始向美國貨報復。」美國貿易代表署（USTR）在8月20到23日，將就有關貨品清單舉行聽證會。一名政府官員表示，需時兩個月來確定最後清單，屆時特朗普將決定新一波加徵關稅措施是否生效。<br />\n<br />\n在政府宣布新舉措後，美國零售業領導者協會（RILA）發聲明指，政府做法將危害美國人，有違特朗普對業界作出「將最大痛苦帶給中國，消費者只會感受最少陣痛」的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部新聞發言人回應時批評，美方的行為傷害中國和全世界，同時傷害其自身，又指這種失去理性的行為是不得人心的。該發言人又指，中方對美方的行為感到震驚，為了維護國家核心利益和人民根本利益，中國政府將一如既往，不得不作出必要反制；中方亦將立即就美方的單邊主義行為向世界貿易組織追加起訴。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上周宣布向總值500億美元（約3900億港元）的中國進口商品徵收25%關稅，打開貿易戰序幕。他曾警告兩周內向另外160億美元（約1248億港元）進口中國產品徵稅，之後又指或追加對2000億美元中國商品徵收10%關稅，反擊中方對美國商品徵報復性關稅。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/mobile/bkn-20180711064741700-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180711064741700-0711_00822_001.html&d=voP7tq0CdGeXI%2FGEQLZGc54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=903dd98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/mobile/bkn-20180711064741700-0711_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d4b2564998b30e92ce8e3846bf50a594a65bec1e","tid":737783,"uid":161125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"把劍呢?"},{"pid":"58d79f44092f3fed30632b1e339d7b06e6c8dc58","tid":737783,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b2564998b30e92ce8e3846bf50a594a65bec1e","tid":737783,"uid":161125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"把劍呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513fd02ae9c893b11e5ef91362d9e5bfe86fb733","tid":737783,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"贏國把劍軟左"},{"pid":"0baac9794e47d4ce859126098107491c9344ea13","tid":737783,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/132755_82bcde3f8c7b449067ac1db4138e38cc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F132755_82bcde3f8c7b449067ac1db4138e38cc.gif&h=c4b07e5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abde82d3496492f8c16ae70c331b699e52852974","tid":737783,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:29:40.000Z","msg":"又講呢啲廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6196e79a1eba1ca3bb057c157fa7fff21a88a8","tid":737783,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3a/Icannotaccept.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091123093558\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3a%2FIcannotaccept.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091123093558&h=23dd0155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1ffb8e09b0d711813d877afe27dabf3d1a64c4","tid":737783,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/133243_9426ade3461a46ffa8e53792cb6f8137.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F0